HEADWORD: Rigsdaler
<hw>Rigs"da`ler</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Dan. See
<er>Rix-dollar</er>.]</ety> <def>A Danish coin worth about fifty-four
cents. It was the former unit of value in Denmark.</def>⟦br⟧
